    howToGetThere: `From Pokhara Lakeside, take a taxi or local bus toward the hills east or north of Phewa Lake (15–25 min). Ask locally for the Jharana Waterfall trail from the nearest village. A short forest walk of 30–45 minutes leads to the falls.`,
