    howToGetThere: `From Pokhara Lakeside, take a taxi or rickshaw north to the K.I. Singh Bridge viewing area (approx. 10 min, 5 km). The gorge viewpoint is accessible from the park near Prithvi Narayan Campus. Ask any local for 'Seti Gorge' or 'K.I. Singh Pool.'`,
