    howToGetThere: `From Kathmandu or Pokhara, travel to Damauli on the Prithvi Highway (approx. 3 hrs from Kathmandu, 2 hrs from Pokhara). From Damauli, hire a local guide or ask guesthouse owners to direct you to Kali Khola gorge trails. A 30–60 min hike leads to the waterfall area.`,
