    bestSeason: `Oct–Nov, Mar–May`,
    openingHours: `Always open`,
    howToGetThere: `Fly from Kathmandu to Bhadrapur (Jhapa) then take a bus or jeep to Phungling/Taplejung (8–10 hrs total). Alternatively, fly direct to Suketar Airport in Taplejung when weather permits. From Phungling, ask locals for Tamor River trail access to the waterfall area.`,
